{"tid":895116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杏花邨油庫「火警」嚇壞街坊","createTime":"2018-11-09T02:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T03:19:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15254f8ccd3891d224145d294df211b9b0887737","tid":895116,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181109/20541790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F20541790&d=G9rguUQjZKtPcM8sTPrYkfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=fdb83c42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F20541790&h=baa1bc21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181109/20541790</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月09日 <br />\n<br />\n杏花邨油庫「火警」嚇壞街坊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181109/large/09la7p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181109%2Flarge%2F09la7p04.jpg&h=eccc3fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n演習模擬油庫發生火警，消防員不斷向火場射水。facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】柴灣杏花邨對開中石化油庫昨早有火警演習，模擬油庫發生火警，多輛消防車抵達現場，消防員架起雲梯射水灌救。有附近居民目睹場面逼真，一度以為發生巨災，虛驚一場，其後油庫於中午恢復運作。<br />\n<br />\n現場是創富道的中石化柴灣油庫，昨早約10時半，消防處聯同油公司進行防火演習，模擬油庫發生火警。由於油庫毗鄰就是杏花邨遊樂場，亦接近民居，消防嚴陣以待，其間疏散油庫職員並拖喉救火，有消防員更架起雲梯射水灌救，從遠處也可見油庫上空出現長長的水柱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出動7架消防車<br />\n<br />\n演習過程中，有附近居民目睹消防大陣仗，一度以為油站火警真有其事，後始知原來虛驚一場。消防處表示共出動7架消防車及26名消防員參與演習，旨在令消防人員及油庫職員熟習現場環境，加強溝通，其間消防員用水灌救，沒有使用化學泡沫。<br />\n<br />\n中石化（香港）油站有限公司表示，今次是柴灣油庫的例行火警演習，每年第4季都會進行，旨在為同事提供在職安全培訓，公司共派出12位同事參與其中，油庫於昨午12時30分恢復運作。<br />\n<br />\n■記者翁鈺輝  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n屋宇署修葺令阻嚇力不足<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n民建聯「成功爭取」避雨亭變撞柱亭　12萬建造11萬補鑊"},{"pid":"41fced2f0d3d9c6857cbe32179a593031e2f6a14","tid":895116,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"杏花邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe05da5436d4f9cd52f35d3710ba6d5c02c01b8f","tid":895116,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"其實真係著火<br />\n廢事嚇親人先咁講"},{"pid":"dff367360992669fd471c5caaa0b9d9a97606349","tid":895116,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"點解油庫著火會用水救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5885e1d676cc0c4fd82ef958b60e3de0909bc4a7","tid":895116,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff367360992669fd471c5caaa0b9d9a97606349","tid":895116,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"點解油庫著火會用水救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"2d80a710d7b27ef6e41629e273a49354ab4fc4d7","tid":895116,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5885e1d676cc0c4fd82ef958b60e3de0909bc4a7","tid":895116,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff367360992669fd471c5caaa0b9d9a97606349","tid":895116,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"點解油庫著火會用水救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"咁攪笑"},{"pid":"92fb2ad6234a04d99e2ad6f6ba000d0ad038d861","tid":895116,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff367360992669fd471c5caaa0b9d9a97606349","tid":895116,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"